popular name for the drug, not just the plant, and that the
information accordingly charged an offense. For this proposition,
it cited dictionaries, other state statutes, articles, cases and
texts. It is the court's familiarity with the articles describing
the allegedly evil effects of the drug with which we are
concerned. </p>

